[Although the case reports are redundant, this summary lays out the current WHO position in Uganda, including its judgment that the level of risk at the national level is currently moderate. Since there is no evidence of local transmission within Uganda, the Emergency Committee may not yet declare a PHEIC at its imminent meeting. - Mod LXL

